    • Constructor Detail

      • URLClassLoader

        public URLClassLoader(Collection<URL> urls,
                      URLStreamHandlerFactory factory)
        Creates a new class loader based on the given URLs. Calls URLClassLoader(Collection, ClassLoader, URLStreamHandlerFactory) with the system class loader as parent.
        Parameters:
        urls - the list of URLs; may not be null or empty and may not contain null entries.
        factory - the optional URLStreamHandlerFactory if some URLs are not otherwise understood by the system.

      • URLClassLoader

        public URLClassLoader(Collection<URL> urls,
                      ClassLoader parent,
                      URLStreamHandlerFactory factory)
        Creates a new class loader based on the given URLs.
        Parameters:
        urls - the list of URLs; may not be null or empty and may not contain null entries.
        parent - the parent class loader to use; may not be null.
        factory - the optional URLStreamHandlerFactory if some URLs are not otherwise understood by the system.
